    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果您在游玩本游戏时发现主角只有狗，说明本作销量不佳。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或是本作销量尚可，但开发者正在偷懒摸鱼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >销量不佳的原因可能是，尽管开发者自诩这款游戏有“容易上手，策略上限高”的优点，却难掩独立开发的贫穷气质。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >尽管如此，《泡泡飘飘》能够提供其他游戏没有的即时消除玩法，带来全新的游玩体验。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >漂浮、碰撞、融合、破裂</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如你所见，没有格子、没有回合，也没有制作经费，《泡泡飘飘》是一款即时消除游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >规则很简单，发射泡泡，同色合并、变大，直到破裂——这将生成新的泡泡，让局面更加复杂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239220/extras/a3ab321251ee16a8b7e703a06d164c72.poster.avif?t=1753335187\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239220/extras/a3ab321251ee16a8b7e703a06d164c72.webm?t=1753335187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239220/extras/a3ab321251ee16a8b7e703a06d164c72.mp4?t=1753335187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >漫游小狗的白日梦</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的一切都是小狗的梦，你能抵达梦的尽头吗……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >什么，为何是狗而不是猫？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开发者试图避免站队，并将此问题归结为缺乏经费。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果游戏卖得出去，不止猫狗，他很乐意为游戏添加一整座动物园。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >显然，狗和游戏开发者都有自己的白日梦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239220/extras/313e0276b56b96ee9bf1a554ea1d1165.poster.avif?t=1753335187\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239220/extras/313e0276b56b96ee9bf1a554ea1d1165.webm?t=1753335187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239220/extras/313e0276b56b96ee9bf1a554ea1d1165.mp4?t=1753335187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >兼具休闲与挑战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >再次强调：游戏既适合休闲游玩，也有不低的操作和策略上限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它可以简单到完全依赖运气，乱按都可能过关；也可以算准每一步，像策略游戏一样精密规划通关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为什么一再强调这点？只因开发者试图同时吸引休闲和重度玩家。但他没有意识到，除他自己外，该游戏所属的新兴领域尚无重度玩家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239220/extras/878a260c407950ee4f28ba4da4cdb4be.poster.avif?t=1753335187\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239220/extras/878a260c407950ee4f28ba4da4cdb4be.webm?t=1753335187\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239220/extras/878a260c407950ee4f28ba4da4cdb4be.mp4?t=1753335187\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富多样的机制和玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个大关卡都是一个全新的世界，这不止意味着场景的变化，还意味着全新的游戏机制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请注意，由于主角的物种限制，无论玩家表现得多好，主角的衣物也不会减少，或突然变身为狗娘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >之所以强调这一点，是因为开发者希望教化前来提问的损友们：客观上并不存在“Steam+消除=脱衣”这样奇怪的等式——至少在这款游戏中，小狗只会掉毛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
